    {"type":"text","id":"p1h","x":10,"y":46,"width":265,"height":18,"text":"PASADA 1 — ¿Es relevante?  (5-10 min)","originalText":"PASADA 1 — ¿Es relevante?  (5-10 min)","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#92400e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":211,"version":1,"versionNonce":212,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"p1c","x":18,"y":68,"width":249,"height":156,"text":"Lee en este orden:\n1. Título\n2. Abstract completo\n3. Introducción (1er párrafo)\n4. Conclusiones\n5. Figuras y tablas\n\nDecisión:\n✓ Relevante → Pasada 2\n✗ No relevante → Descartar\n? Incierto → Guarda, revisita\n\nMeta: evaluar si vale\nla inversión de tiempo.","originalText":"Lee en este orden:\n1. Título\n2. Abstract completo\n3. Introducción (1er párrafo)\n4. Conclusiones\n5. Figuras y tablas\n\nDecisión:\n✓ Relevante → Pasada 2\n✗ No relevante → Descartar\n? Incierto → Guarda, revisita\n\nMeta: evaluar si vale\nla inversión de tiempo.","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#92400e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":221,"version":1,"versionNonce":222,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.4},

